{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And being, I guess, that he developed good relation with us, the people in the village somehow tolerated us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if everybody knew, or who knew, or who whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he was helping us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he sent us a Polish doctor who was in that village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this doctor was coming, and visiting with me, and was helping my mother during the typhoid, and my uncle during the typhoid, and me with-- with this rheumatic fever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was giving me some kind of a medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after half a year, I started to learn how to hold a cup in my hand again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like completely new experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember, when I made my first step after that, I was like a baby who was-- you know, who is 18 months old and starts to walk.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Somebody had to stand in front of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was making steps and running to that person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The person would be catching me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's how finally I got back on my feet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember which house we were in, but somewhere, in somebody's house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what had happened is that when we were in these villages, every so often, you know, the Poles would come to us, that we were staying with or that were helping us-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would say, I think the Germans-- the Germans are coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when that was, we had to run to the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, some other group of Jews-- or maybe that was the one that we were, you know, in contact with.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't really remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had built already a winter structure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because sometimes we had to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
